# Daily Grass Tracker

## Overview
The Daily Grass Tracker is a project designed to help users monitor and track the growth and health of their grass.

## Features
- Daily measurements of grass height
- Health indicators for grass
- Graphical representation of growth over time

## Getting Started
To get started with the Daily Grass Tracker, clone the repository and follow the instructions in the setup guide.

